Author: SemicolonButterfly
Text: I’d trade...except sounds like we’re in similar boats. My upper body is roughly two sizes smaller than my lower body, which like...I can’t even. My butt/hips/thighs consume so much of my  attention and loathingggg. Pants shopping is hell. (I go with A-line dresses sometimes because then I can just size for my torso, which is way less upsetting.)
